    "riv.exchange — P2P watch trading with verified provenance": "riv.exchange —— 提供具完整溯源驗證的點對點手錶交易。",
    "Luxury watches are RIVEX's Tier 1 launch category — transparent pricing, high liquidity, and a $29B pre-owned market with no unified authentication standard make them the ideal first collateral asset. APAC accounts for 42% of demand, aligning perfectly with RIVEX's HK-first strategy.": "奢侈手錶會是 RIVEX 的第一層起步品類。它同時具備價格透明、流動性高，以及 290 億美元二手市場卻缺乏統一認證標準這三個條件，因此是最理想的首發抵押品類；而亞太占全球需求約 42%，也與 RIVEX 以香港為起點的策略高度一致。",

