    "None offer unified authentication + lending + trading infrastructure": "但目前沒有任何一方能同時提供統一認證、借貸與交易的完整基建。",
    "Fine Art holds 33% of UHNWI collectible wealth (~$853B) yet annual transaction volume is only $67.8B — a 6.7% turnover rate. The art-backed lending market ($28–33B) represents <4% penetration of the available stock, making it RIVEX's largest single lending opportunity.": "藝術品占超高淨值收藏財富約 33%，規模約 8,530 億美元，但年交易量只有 678 億美元，周轉率僅 6.7%。現有藝術品抵押借貸市場僅約 280 至 330 億美元，占可用資產存量不到 4%，因此是 RIVEX 最大的單一借貸機會。",

