    "RIVEX Origin — Bottle-level Digital Passport; storage condition logging; anti-counterfeiting": "RIVEX Origin —— 為每瓶酒建立數位護照，記錄存放條件並強化防偽。",
    "riv.cash — Wine cellar as collateral; LTV up to 80% on verified collections": "riv.cash —— 以酒窖收藏作為抵押，對已驗證資產提供最高 80% LTV。",
    "riv.exchange — P2P wine trading with verified provenance and storage history": "riv.exchange —— 提供具完整溯源與倉儲紀錄的點對點酒品交易。",
