    "Fine wine is in an early recovery cycle after a 2-year correction — historically the most attractive entry point. HK demand is returning and trade restocking is visible. The €99B market has no unified digital provenance standard, creating a clear RIVEX authentication and lending opportunity.": "精品葡萄酒市場在經歷兩年修正後，正進入早期復甦週期，而這往往也是歷史上最有吸引力的切入區間。香港需求正在回流，通路補庫存跡象明顯；但這個 990 億歐元的市場仍沒有統一的數位溯源標準，RIVEX 因此擁有清晰的認證與借貸切入機會。",

