    "Compressed from 100% peak. Volume-driven market; 50+ pairs/month for profitability.": "已從高峰期動輒 100% 的利差回落，目前更偏向高周轉、重規模的市場，通常需每月成交 50 雙以上才更容易穩定獲利。",
    "Authentication at scale — No universal standard for sneaker verification; RIVEX Origin can provide on-chain Digital Passport for graded/authenticated pairs": "規模化認證是關鍵 —— 球鞋市場至今沒有統一驗證標準，RIVEX Origin 可以為經鑑定的鞋款建立鏈上數位護照。",
    "Mass-market entry point — Lower price points vs. art/watches; drives rivex.app user acquisition and data flywheel": "適合作為大眾市場入口 —— 相比藝術品與手錶，球鞋價格帶更低，更有利於推動 rivex.app 的用戶增長與數據飛輪。",
    "Platforms: StockX, GOAT, Alias, Grailed — none offer unified provenance + lending": "代表平台包括 StockX、GOAT、Alias、Grailed，但目前沒有任何一方同時提供統一溯源與借貸能力。",
