    "Grading standardization — PSA/BGS grading is centralized and slow; RIVEX can offer faster on-chain certification with third-party grader integration": "評級標準化仍有空間 —— PSA / BGS 的評級體系集中、流程偏慢，RIVEX 可透過第三方整合提供更快的鏈上認證。",
    "High-value card lending — PSA 10 Pokémon and sports cards can be worth $10K–$5M+; riv.cash can unlock liquidity": "高價卡片借貸需求存在 —— PSA 10 等級的寶可夢卡與運動卡，價格可從 1 萬美元一路到 500 萬美元以上，riv.cash 能把這些價值轉化為流動性。",
    "Platforms: PSA, BGS, eBay, PWCC, TCGPlayer — no unified finance layer": "代表平台包括 PSA、BGS、eBay、PWCC、TCGPlayer，但市場仍缺乏統一的金融層。",
    "Sneakers and TCG represent RIVEX's mass-market acquisition funnel — lower price points drive rivex.app user growth and data flywheel, while high-value graded cards and rare sneakers unlock riv.cash lending. The $33B sports card market growing at 22% CAGR is one of the fastest-growing collectible categories.": "球鞋與 TCG 會成為 RIVEX 面向大眾市場的獲客漏斗。較低的價格帶有助於推動 rivex.app 的用戶增長與數據飛輪，而高價評級卡與稀有球鞋則能進一步解鎖 riv.cash 借貸。以 22% 年複合成長率成長的 330 億美元運動卡市場，更是目前增速最快的收藏品類之一。",

