    "APAC Share of Luxury Demand": "亞太奢侈品需求占比",
    "APAC remains a core growth engine for luxury resale and cross-border secondary trading.": "亞太依然是奢侈品轉售與跨境二級交易的核心成長引擎。",
    "The Core Problem": "核心問題",
    "Authentication is fragmented — trust still relies on platform-specific experts and closed databases": "認證體系仍然割裂 —— 市場信任仍高度依賴平台自有專家與封閉資料庫。",
    "No portable identity — authenticity, condition, and repair history rarely travel with the bag": "缺乏可攜式身份標準 —— 真偽、品相與維修紀錄往往無法隨資產一起流通。",
    "Luxury resale has liquidity, but limited financial utility — no standardized collateral layer exists": "奢侈品轉售雖有流動性，卻仍缺乏金融用途 —— 市場尚未形成可規模化的標準化抵押層。",
    "RIVEX Origin — Bag-level Digital Passport with authentication, condition, and ownership history": "RIVEX Origin —— 為每只手袋建立數位護照，整合真偽、品相與持有歷史。",
    "riv.cash — Verified handbags as collateral; unlock liquidity without forced sale": "riv.cash —— 讓已驗證手袋成為抵押品，在不必被迫出售的前提下解鎖流動性。",
    "riv.exchange — P2P resale with verified provenance and standardized trust layer": "riv.exchange —— 提供具完整溯源與標準化信任層的點對點轉售交易。",
