    "Luxury handbags sit at the intersection of fashion, status, and financial value. The market is already liquid, but identity and provenance remain platform-specific. RIVEX can turn handbags from resale products into standardized financial assets.": "奢侈手袋正處於時尚、身份象徵與金融價值的交會點。這個市場本身已有流動性，但身份與溯源仍綁定在各自平台內；RIVEX 的角色，就是把手袋從可轉售商品，進一步變成可標準化處理的金融資產。",

