    "No APAC-native platform offers unified authentication, collateral lending, and exchange infrastructure across collectibles.": "目前沒有任何亞太原生平台，能同時提供跨品類的認證、抵押借貸與交易基建。",
    "Why APAC First": "為何先做亞太",
    "APAC combines dense collector networks, cross-border capital, luxury demand, and weak infrastructure standardization — exactly where RIVEX creates the most leverage.": "亞太同時具備高密度收藏圈、跨境資金流、強烈奢侈品需求，以及基礎設施標準化不足這四個條件，也正是 RIVEX 最能放大槓桿的地方。",
    "Hong Kong as launchpad — trusted legal framework, free port dynamics, dense collector and dealer networks": "以香港作為發射台 —— 擁有成熟法治、自由港優勢，以及密集的收藏家與經銷商網絡。",
    "Mainland + Taiwan + SEA expansion — cultural affinity and Chinese collector capital create natural adjacency": "向中國內地、台灣與東南亞擴張 —— 文化相近、華人收藏資本流動性高，天然具備延伸性。",
    "Luxury + mass collectible overlap — APAC is strong in watches, handbags, wine, TCG, and cross-border resale": "高端與大眾收藏交疊 —— 亞太在手錶、手袋、葡萄酒、TCG 與跨境轉售上都具備強勢需求。",
    "RIVEX can become the default infrastructure layer before Western incumbents localize.": "在西方既有玩家完成在地化之前，RIVEX 有機會先成為預設基礎設施層。",
    "APAC is not just a launch market; it is where RIVEX can define the regional standard first. The region has demand, wealth, and collector density, but lacks a native infrastructure player that bridges authentication, lending, and exchange.": "亞太不只是 RIVEX 的首發市場，更是最有機會率先定義區域標準的地方。這裡同時具備需求、財富與收藏密度，但仍缺少一個能打通認證、借貸與交易的原生基建平台。",

